rows.label: tlk41100171_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Woo-hoo!
I'm really raking it in today!

rows.label: tlk41100171_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The tourists at Milama Viewpoint toss
their coins into the Cloud Sea, but
some of them land around here!

rows.label: tlk41100171_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Tossing a coin's supposed to grant
you a wish. Well it sure granted my
wish...to earn more money, that is!

rows.label: tlk41100171_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Why don't you have a go too?
If you happen to throw it my way,
I'll save it for a rainy day!
